<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🧊 M003 Extension 2 — English Worksheet (Beginner)</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Pixel-Art Mob Heads (x, y) · <strong>Course:</strong> 3D Coordinates · <strong>Level:</strong> Extension (Beginner, after Week 3) · <strong>Time:</strong> about 30 minutes</p>
<p>Copy a mob head with <strong>(x, y)</strong>. x is <strong>across</strong>, y is <strong>up</strong>. The heads already stand in front of you in the world — look at them as you build.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>🔴 Stand on your <strong>home spot</strong> (red block) every run. Move, and the picture moves too.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Predict 🔮</h2>
<p>Read the steps. Circle or write your answer.</p>
<pre><code>place green block at (4, 11)
place green block at (5, 11)
place green block at (6, 11)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>A line across? Circle one:</strong> across · up</p>
<p><strong>Which number stays the same — x or y?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<pre><code>place black block at (6, 6)
place black block at (6, 7)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Share x = 6, y grows. Circle one:</strong> across · up</p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>2 · Find the Difference 🐛</h2>
<p><strong>Correct</strong> first, then <strong>broken</strong>. Write one sentence about the bug.</p>
<p><strong>Pair A</strong> — Creeper eyes: (4, 11) and (10, 11).</p>
<pre><code># correct
place black block at (4, 11)
place black block at (10, 11)
</code></pre>
<pre><code># broken
place black block at (4, 11)
place black block at (4, 11)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>What is wrong? Where do both land?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Pair B</strong> — Piglin eye: (5, 10).</p>
<pre><code># correct
place dark block at (5, 10)
</code></pre>
<pre><code># broken
place dark block at (10, 5)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>What is wrong? Which numbers got swapped?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>3 · Fill the Gap ✏️</h2>
<p>To go <strong>up</strong>, the <strong>second</strong> number (y) grows. Fill the blanks to go up at x = 6.</p>
<pre><code>place black block at (6, 6)
place black block at (6, __)
place black block at (6, __)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Word bank:</strong> <code>7</code> · <code>8</code></p>
<p><strong>Write the two numbers:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>4 · Tell Me What You Built 📸</h2>
<p><strong>Warm up.</strong> Copy this mini creeper face. Read each square's (x, y).</p>
